Green_Bay.Ashwaubenon High School:
Ashwaubenon High School is a high school in Ashwaubenon, Wisconsin, a suburb of Green Bay.


== Academics ==
Ashwaubenon High School offers Advanced Placement (AP) classes, such as United States history, art history, statistics, chemistry, biology, psychology, calculus I/II and U.S. government. It also offers Youth Options programs, which give students an opportunity to work and learn in areas of interest during a portion of the school day.
